release_notes:
Our initial V1 release of the macOS WARP Client! A huge thank you to all the beta testers who helped us get here.

**Notable V1 features**

Support for Cloudflare for Teams.
- All supported modes from our mobile client (1.1.1.1, 1.1.1.1 for Families, WARP, WARP+, WARP Unlimited).
- Ability to exclude wireless and wired networks from WARP.
- Ability to copy WARP Unlimited license from your iOS or Android device.


**Known issues**

- You are unable to subscribe to WARP+ via the Desktop apps. You must subscribe first on your mobile device and then copy/paste your license key into the Accounts page on desktop.
- Localization parity with mobile is coming in a future update.
- DNS Logs are not yet implemented.
- Wired networks via a USB dongle are not excluded properly.

For a complete list of known issues please visit https://developers.cloudflare.com/warpclient/known-issues-and-faq
